  "title": "Devotional: Reflection on Psalm 117:1–2",
  "body": "Praise the LORD, all nations! Glorify Him, all peoples! For His faithful love to us is great; the LORD’s faithfulness endures forever. Hallelujah!\n\nThis psalm, though the shortest, holds the highest call — that all nations would glorify God for His unending mercy and faithfulness. It is a reminder that salvation is not limited but offered to all.",
